{"type": "article", "id": 12859, "title": "Bang & Olufsen 90 周年纪念系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-31T07:34:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000212E5t8zBw6KisnrRfq.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今年是顶级视听品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 成立 90 周年，为此他们近日推出了新的 The Love Affair Collection 限量版产品。精选了品牌历史上 8 款经典设计，包括耳机，电视，音响等，打造了一个玫瑰金系列，玫瑰金铝材搭配干净优雅的胡桃木，看上去非常美丽。这是<a href=\"http://www.bang-olufsen.com/en/loveaffaircollection\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614054692KGMymwU36fln4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5654649\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140546ZH0stXgbWeqAY42m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.55287009\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140547yMdmeiYuphxbB1nA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140547mhXKw9AkcJPd1sqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405482twDfynC3cxk0SK8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140548oGwTPtSdC9cmKAzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}